   <div class="index-section">
    <div class="page-width">
     <div class="custom-content section-spacing-padding section-spacing--disable-top">
      <div class="custom__item small--one-whole one-half align--top-middle">
       <div class="custom__item-inner custom__item-inner--liquid">
        <div class="rte">
         <h3 class="desktop-only__heading">
          LATTICE COLLECTION
         </h3>
         <h6>
          Defined Edges, Expansive Horizons
         </h6>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="custom__item small--one-whole one-half align--top-middle">
       <div class="custom__item-inner custom__item-inner--liquid">
        <div class="rte">
         <div class="content__inner rte">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
           A pattern embodies one's self-acceptance and inner balance.
          </p>
         </div>
         <div class="content__inner rte1">
          <div class="hide-div readless" style="display: none;">
           <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
            <strong style="display: block; padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px;">
             Defined Edges, Expansive Horizons
            </strong>
           </p>
           <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
            The Lattice Collection traces its structure in leather and speaks through geometry. Each bag forms its own world, connected through structure and craft.
           </p>
           <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
            Inspired by the murals of the Kizil Caves in Xinjiang, the layered diamond compositions echo both fragments of time and extensions of space. Their rhythm and repetition portray the movement and the richness of everyday life.
           </p>
           <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
            Songmont brings this ancient visual language through modern craftsmanship. Using a whole full-grain leather panel construction and hand-threaded weaving techniques, this collection rebuilds dimensional structure and creating depth through light and shadow.
           </p>
           <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
            Each Lattice woven leather tote bag is more than a work bag for daily commute, but an expression of perspective, accepting different sides of yourself, keeping your edge, allowing strength and softness to coexist.
           </p>
           <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
            Structure meets suppleness. Precision carries warmth.
           </p>
           <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
            Carry your world in a Songmont carry on bag.
           </p>
           <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
            Let the journeys you take fill each diamond panel with memory, intention, and quiet ambition, expanding into spaces that are entirely your own.
           </p>
          </div>
          <button class="readmore-trigger1" onclick="toggleReadMore1(this)" type="button">
           <p>
            Read More
           </p>
          </button>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
